import React from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'

class NavBar extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <React.Fragment>
                <Menu>
                    <NavLink to='/' exact>
                            <Menu.Item name='logo'>CineSearch</Menu.Item>
                    </NavLink>
                    <Menu.Item
                        name='editorials'
                        
                        >
                        Editorials
                    </Menu.Item>
            
                    <Menu.Item
                        name='reviews'
                    
                        >
                        Reviews
                    </Menu.Item>
            
                    <Menu.Item
                        name='upcomingEvents'
                    
                        >
                        Upcoming Events
                    </Menu.Item>
                </Menu>
            </React.Fragment>
        
        )
    }
}

export default NavBar
